{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-index-js","path":"/","result":{"data":{"hero":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Hello World! My name is","name":"Navin Seab","subtitle":"Make thing simple and fun!","buttonText":"Contact Me"},"html":"<p>I am a software engineering student with a strong passion for AI/ML, seeking to combine my technical skills with cutting-edge technologies to create innovative solutions</p>\n<p>I am currently employed as a Fullstack Data Scientist at <a href=\"https://www.ababank.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ABA Bank</a> , where I have the opportunity to leverage my expertise in data science and software development within the banking industry.</p>\n<p>Outside work, I occasionally blog on <a href=\"https://medium.com/@seabgreatnavin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Medium</a>.and  <a href=\"https://www.kaggle.com/navinseab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Kaggle</a>!</p>"}}]},"about":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"About Me","avatar":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/bfaca252f72179ef78f8a787a1589ebf/3d39a/navin.jpg","srcSet":"/static/bfaca252f72179ef78f8a787a1589ebf/477ba/navin.jpg 175w,\n/static/bfaca252f72179ef78f8a787a1589ebf/06776/navin.jpg 350w,\n/static/bfaca252f72179ef78f8a787a1589ebf/3d39a/navin.jpg 432w","srcWebp":"/static/bfaca252f72179ef78f8a787a1589ebf/d9974/navin.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/bfaca252f72179ef78f8a787a1589ebf/9fca7/navin.webp 175w,\n/static/bfaca252f72179ef78f8a787a1589ebf/37a4e/navin.webp 350w,\n/static/bfaca252f72179ef78f8a787a1589ebf/d9974/navin.webp 432w","sizes":"(max-width: 432px) 100vw, 432px"}}},"skills":["Programming => Python / Javascript/ Typescript /Java","Backend => Flask / Node.js / Nest.js, Django, FastAPI","ML lib => Scikitlearn,Spacy / NLTK / OPENCV","Deep learning => Tensorflow / Bert / GPT","FrontEnd => Html / css, javascript / boostrap / apexchart","Data scrapping => Scrapy / BeautifulSoup / Selenuim","Database => MSSQL/Postgres/Mysql/Firebase/MongoDB","","Devops=> Docker/aws/GCP"]},"html":"<p>I am an accomplished self-taught AI/ML engineer and Backend Developer, I have been working in a variety range of areas in the tech industry for around 3 years from Data Science, AI, Mobile app, and Backend</p>\n<!-- I'm currently working as a developer for **Bell Canada** in the Amdocs Digital Delivery unit. My responsibilty includes Java/Spring based microservices development & testing. \r\n\r\nI'm also an [Innovation Agent](https://drive.google.com/file/d/117KS9QnDrcg7dllcAzGz_b7qQPgR3pGs/view?usp=sharing) fostering the culture of creativity and innovation at Amdocs, India.\r\n\r\nI have been awarded as Winner in [Innovation Nugget](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PzTZkXlQV9ldZxqmBbbO94uIqrhSwvcq/view?usp=sharing), Creativity Jam, [Design Thinking Hackathon](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hXCATvKwzHCvctHtElsqFg5YIqabz22O/view?usp=sharing) and Runners-Up in [Project ICE Fair](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1exB19OoQ5dzU2mg4qbdkNutA25TGBWV3/view?usp=sharing) by Amdocs. -->\n<p>Here is a list of the technologies that I'm familiar with!</p>"}}]},"jobs":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Fullstack Data scientist","company":"ABA Bank","range":"August 2022 - Present","url":"https://www.ababank.com/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p>working on various technology from ML model building, model deployment, model testing and API development</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Woring on data scrapping , and automation</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Build fraud detection , using graph algorithm and ML algorithm</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Collaborat with <a href=\"\">Visa analytic team</a> to build Recommendation engine, Fraud detection</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Use python, PowerBI, docker, SQL, Gitlab, Tensorflow, GPT3, BERT</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Software Developer/Machine learning engineer","company":"V-Tech","range":"May 2021 - June 2022","url":"https://www.vtech.one/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p>work with machine learning and deep learning</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Build a bad post detection using NLP, Deep Learning, and Machine learning to delete any inappropriate post from <a href=\"https://goop.ai/feed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">goop</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Build a computer vision application that allows the user to fit their face in other people’s clothes</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Build a trading bot for the Chinese stock market, which includes back-testing and development of trading strategy using python and machine learning</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Build a voice changer and transformation, allows users to talk through a virtual microphone and change their voice in real-time, can be used in any software (google meet, zoom, Microsoft team)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Team Lead/ Backend-dev","company":"KIT core-member","range":"July 2020 - August 2020","url":"https://kit.edu.kh/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Work on a lot of technology: nest.js, express, python, web3, blockchain</li>\n<li>Web3 Development: build smart contract and back-end for NFT (trading bot)</li>\n<li>Working on data scrapping, and visualization for a Japanese client company</li>\n<li>Build Backend and API for Covid19 tracking app (published in play store and app store)</li>\n<li>Build Backend and API for job matching application (more like tinder but focus on the job)</li>\n<li>Working on data storing and server scheduling for a client company</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"President/ Android developer","company":"InTech","range":"Sept 2020 - Oct 2021","url":""},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Lead and Manage a virtual company in KIT</li>\n<li>IntTech virtual Company, we are focused on AI face recognition, our mission is to implement face recognition into any type of application like mobile app, web app, etc.</li>\n<li>Build temperature and attendance checking app using face recognition and machine learning (request by <a href=\"https://www.misti.gov.kh/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">MISTI</a>)</li>\n<li>You can see the demo video <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1uX6LhAgRCvVmoY6TA16ni44W_GURolZb/view?usp=share_link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a></li>\n<li>You can also download our application <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1k5BMqn2o36vPO1BKrck97-aDDC1UinXR/view?usp=share_link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Team lead / Backend Developer / ML engineer","company":"Freelencing","range":"Sept 2020 - Oct 2021","url":""},"html":"<ul>\n<li>We build a team that help local businesses and startup in Cambodia to build their prototype, products that related to tech industry, include webApp, MobileApp, AI and Data science applications.</li>\n<li>lottery app : Cambodian client</li>\n<li>Medicine recognition: use OCR in mobile app to identify the medicine , see the demo application <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1NBVTFLTJ1cn8lkdoXYNczrWxeuHrQlt4/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a></li>\n<li>Medicine E-commerce allow pharmaacist to sell medicine and services in our application , you can see the demo <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gZLkhNYS5QhqRR2YGdmld7lFPKTVQ-Vj/view?usp=share_link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Research and Development","company":"Competition","range":"May - June 2018","url":""},"html":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1VODCcQ-jpBcPZ16YeJ7RC0qdbq7xgXEO/view?usp=share_link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Smart start cycle 4</a> , I lead the team and get into final pitch of our business idea and application</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1W21rbb7erjnoiTiVR7stlAtwbMNnaswN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">AWS build on Cambodia</a>, I lead the team and our application got first runner up. you can view certicate <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Atfu6KA6mutr2p58THb3JXvefzNciwSm/view?usp=share_link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/14tL5lbDmJPRuUGj5cPsGCH4B4WiZyp9r/view?usp=share_link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Tech no innovation Cmbodia</a> , we build an application that allow farmer to take photo of rice disease and our application able to detect the desease and provide solution, you can see the demo <a href=\"https://youtu.be/R-pLtriQstQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a>, see certification <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1wIsWJyEtSAgMm1uZlFLeKzHz5TgwrepB/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://sites.google.com/paragoniu.edu.kh/cscup\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CS CUP 2021</a> is an annual competitive programming competition where high school and university students compete against each other through 4 rounds of challenges in which starting from 24 May 2021 to 20 June 2021. I join this and got into top 15 in coding.</li>\n</ul>"}}]},"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Temperature and attendance checking","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.7676767676767677,"src":"/static/faaf628c3bbcb28ae24f26ad528dcb0b/acb0d/temp.png","srcSet":"/static/faaf628c3bbcb28ae24f26ad528dcb0b/847ef/temp.png 175w,\n/static/faaf628c3bbcb28ae24f26ad528dcb0b/91cba/temp.png 350w,\n/static/faaf628c3bbcb28ae24f26ad528dcb0b/acb0d/temp.png 643w","srcWebp":"/static/faaf628c3bbcb28ae24f26ad528dcb0b/87201/temp.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/faaf628c3bbcb28ae24f26ad528dcb0b/9fca7/temp.webp 1