/medium.com/@seabgreatnavin/deep-learning-image-classification-application-part2-model-building-39e43d5f5c6"},"html":"<p>In the rainy season there are a lot of mushroom in our <a href=\"https://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g729357-d3804229-Reviews-Kirirom_National_Park-Kampong_Speu_Kampong_Speu_Province.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">college area(KIT)</a>, And when we have free time we went to collect mushroom in the forest but we are not sure which mushroom is dangerous or poisonous. That’s why I try to build a mobile application based on AI that can classify if the mushroom is poisonous by just taking a photo of the mushroom more importantly it can work even in offline mode.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Customer CX J-trust royal bank, AWS","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3779527559055118,"src":"/static/4b7127e314e8f9305df7127a0da7093a/60290/aws.png","srcSet":"/static/4b7127e314e8f9305df7127a0da7093a/847ef/aws.png 175w,\n/static/4b7127e314e8f9305df7127a0da7093a/91cba/aws.png 350w,\n/static/4b7127e314e8f9305df7127a0da7093a/60290/aws.png 700w,\n/static/4b7127e314e8f9305df7127a0da7093a/f5f50/aws.png 1050w,\n/static/4b7127e314e8f9305df7127a0da7093a/c8ae8/aws.png 1052w","srcWebp":"/static/4b7127e314e8f9305df7127a0da7093a/89afa/aws.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/4b7127e314e8f9305df7127a0da7093a/9fca7/aws.webp 175w,\n/static/4b7127e314e8f9305df7127a0da7093a/37a4e/aws.webp 350w,\n/static/4b7127e314e8f9305df7127a0da7093a/89afa/aws.webp 700w,\n/static/4b7127e314e8f9305df7127a0da7093a/78e7a/aws.webp 1050w,\n/static/4b7127e314e8f9305df7127a0da7093a/aa592/aws.webp 1052w","sizes":"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"}}},"tech":["Python","Machine learning","AWS(sagemaker,ec2,s3)","DOCER"],"github":"https://github.com/seabnavin19/ReadMe.ai","external":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AAkNyZlUae0https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Atfu6KA6mutr2p58THb3JXvefzNciwSm/view?usp=share_link"}